         <div xml:id="main">
            <head type="incipit">
               <supplied reason="XTF-compatibility"> ¶ [The Town Clerk read a letter from Baron Von Mueller stating the specimen of thistle sent to him by S. T. Avery, Belfast, ¶ Now Port Fairy, Vic. ¶  ¶ was the true ¶  ¶ carduus lanceolatus ¶ , and g...</supplied>
            </head>
            <p rend="number" xml:lang="en">87.02.00</p>
            <p rend="correspondent" xml:lang="en">To Frederick Mandeville</p>
            <space dim="vertical" unit="lines" quantity="1"/>
            <space dim="vertical" unit="lines" quantity="1"/>
            <p rend="letter"
               style="font-size: 12pt; hyphenate: false; "
               xml:lang="en">
               <note type="footnote" xml:id="_ftn0" n="1">
                  <p rend="FootnoteText"
                     style="margin-left: 0.3333in; text-indent: -0.3333in; font-size: 9pt; hyphenate: false; "
                     xml:lang="en">
                     <space dim="horizontal" extent="tab"/>Letter not found. The text given here is from a report of the meeting of the Belfast Borough Council on 9 February 1887, in<space unit="chars" quantity="1"/>
                     <seg rend="DefaultParagraphFont" style="font-style: italic; ">Belfast gazette</seg>, 11 February 1887, p. 2. For a briefer report, see Minute book 9, 27 Sep 1886 - 24 Sep 1890, p. 49,<space unit="chars" quantity="1"/>VPRS 11097/P0001, Council Minutes, Belfast Borough Council records, VA 4030, Public Record Office, Victoria.</p>
               </note>
               <space dim="horizontal" extent="tab"/>[The Town Clerk read a letter from Baron Von Mueller stating the specimen of thistle sent to him by S. T. Avery, Belfast,<seg rend="FootnoteReference" style="">
                  <note type="footnote" xml:id="_ftn1" n="2">
                     <p rend="FootnoteText"
                        style="margin-left: 0.3333in; text-indent: -0.3333in; font-size: 9pt; hyphenate: false; "
                        xml:lang="en">
                        <space unit="chars" quantity="1"/>
                        <space dim="horizontal" extent="tab"/>Now Port Fairy, Vic.</p>
                  </note>
               </seg>
               <space unit="chars" quantity="1"/>was the true<space unit="chars" quantity="1"/>
               <seg rend="DefaultParagraphFont" style="font-style: italic; ">carduus lanceolatus</seg>, and gave some information as to the best method of destroying same.]<seg rend="FootnoteReference" style="">
                  <note type="footnote" xml:id="_ftn2" n="3">
                     <p rend="FootnoteText"
                        style="margin-left: 0.3333in; text-indent: -0.3333in; font-size: 9pt; hyphenate: false; "
                        xml:lang="en">
                        <space unit="chars" quantity="1"/>
                        <space dim="horizontal" extent="tab"/>The report continued:’<space unit="chars" quantity="1"/>The specimen was the identical thistle which was placed in the hands of Mr McMeekin, who is an expert and had sworn to it being the<space unit="chars" quantity="1"/>
                        <seg rend="DefaultParagraphFont" style="font-style: italic; ">carduus lanceolatus</seg>. <space unit="chars" quantity="1"/>The Mayor remarked that the letter was from one of the greatest botanists in the colony, and he considered the document was a very valuable one, and he was pleased to have it before the Council.' The<space unit="chars" quantity="1"/>
                        <seg rend="DefaultParagraphFont" style="font-style: italic; ">Gazette</seg>
                        <space unit="chars" quantity="1"/>went on to report a discussion of thistle cases in the local court. 'Cr Earle remarked that in future cases the better plan would be to obtain the services of Baron Von Mueller as a witness and then the offenders would have to pay the expenses'.</p>
                  </note>
               </seg>
            </p>
            <space dim="vertical" unit="lines" quantity="1"/>
            <p rend="plantnames"
               style="font-style: italic; font-size: 10pt; hyphenate: false; "
               xml:lang="en">Carduus lanceolatus</p>
            <space dim="vertical" unit="lines" quantity="1"/>
         </div>
      </body>
   </text>
